Detailed Description

The WNDefinitionViewDelegate protocol declares the interface that must be implemented by WNDefinitionView delegates.

didNavigateToURL: (NSURL *)  URL 
[optional]

Sent when the user navigates to an internet-based URL.

The delegate may choose to open the MobileSafari application, or alternatively, display the web page directly in the application's UI.

Parameters:
definitionViewThe sending definition view.
URLThe URL to which the user has attempted to navigate.
